item.title: A new Squash shop in Town
item.description:
A new Squash shop in Town

Have you always been looking for where to string your racquet? Try that pair of shoes that you saw online. Hit with a racquet before you buy it. It is all now possible with Squash Shop by Sport-Hive. You can come to the newly open Capitol Hill Sport & Health to enjoy all types of Squash gear. We are looking forward to see you there. Contact us at squashshop@sport-hive.com

item.title: SportHive Squash Shop - You just found your next squash gear locally
item.description:
SportHive Squash Shop - You just found your next squash gear locally

Squashive believe in growing Squash. With Squashive you are buying from local proshop. Supporting pros and clubs all over. Be part of the community.
